## Backend Changes Made

### 1. New `scan_frontend_files()` function (lines ~2692-2742)
- Proper TSX/TS file enumeration with correct `find` syntax using grouped expressions `\( -name "*.tsx" -o -name "*.ts" \)`
- Excludes `node_modules`, `dist`, `build` directories using `-prune`
- Returns JSON with separate counts: `tsx_count`, `ts_count`, `total_count`, `test_count`
- **Feature module breakdown**: counts files per feature directory (dashboard, documents, printers, auth, agents, settings, jobs, devices)

### 2. Updated `diagnose_project()` function
- Now uses detected `FRONTEND_DIR` (defaults to `web/dashboard`) instead of hardcoded `frontend/src`
